    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大家好，我是一名单人独立开发者，希望你们喜欢这款游戏。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eva Platformer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏说明</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到游戏 Eva Platformer！在这款游戏中，您将扮演女主角伊娃，在明亮多彩的世界中展开一段激动人心的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的目标是收集金币和钥匙来解锁新的关卡，并在通往胜利的道路上克服各种障碍。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/a4786a858c9dfdbc430937c925672a3c.poster.avif?t=1764937733\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/a4786a858c9dfdbc430937c925672a3c.webm?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/a4786a858c9dfdbc430937c925672a3c.mp4?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集金币： 每个关卡都有数十枚金币等着你去收集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找钥匙：钥匙是通过游戏所需的主要元素。您可以用它们打开通往下一个地点的门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡： 游戏有几个不同的关卡，每个关卡都有独特的地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >障碍和敌人：伊娃在途中会遇到敌人。使用跳跃和攻击消灭他们，达到目标。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/128ebf353699dc6b3f1b807b4ce7a9ed.poster.avif?t=1764937733\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/128ebf353699dc6b3f1b807b4ce7a9ed.webm?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/128ebf353699dc6b3f1b807b4ce7a9ed.mp4?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>帮助伊娃收集所有金币和钥匙，打开通往精彩冒险世界的大门！加入 Eva Platformer 游戏，证明你是真正的平台游戏爱好者！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/0e9c2ffe664401c76fe08032de8136cd.poster.avif?t=1764937733\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/0e9c2ffe664401c76fe08032de8136cd.webm?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176450/extras/0e9c2ffe664401c76fe08032de8136cd.mp4?t=1764937733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
